-- Harrods May Open Store on Shanghai's Riverside Bund, China Daily Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-22T23:04:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/harrods-may-open-store-on-shanghai-s-riverside-bund-china-daily-reports.html

          
          
             Harrods Department Store Co. is in
talks with the municipal government about opening a store on
Shanghai’s Bund, the China Daily reported, citing an
unidentified real estate agent familiar with the plan.  
 It would be the retailer’s first store outside of the U.K.,
the report said.  
          
          


  


        